snippet.title: Taaza Khabar | Season 2 | Official Trailer | Hotstar Specials | Sept 27 | BB Ki Vines Productions
snippet.description:
Don't forget to watch the series "Taaza Khabar" starring Bhuvan Bam, streaming exclusively on Disney+ Hotstar! http://www.hotstar.com/1260127221

Karza aur gunah chukaane padhte hain! Kabhi kabhi marr ke bhi..

Vardaan ya shraap? Kismat ya mehnat? Jeevan ya maut?
Vasya ki kahani ka naya adhyay dekhiye Hotstar Specials Taaza Khabar Season 2 mein, streaming from September 27, only on Disney+ Hotstar.

Disney+ Hotstar's hit fantasy-drama series returns with Hotstar Specials presents Taaza Khabar Season 2, diving deeper into the consequences of Vasya's miraculous gift. Set against the gritty backdrop of Mumbai, this season promises to take viewers on an intense journey as Vasya grapples with the loss of his power and faces life-threatening challenges.

Directed by Himank Gaur and produced by Rohit Raj & Bhuvan Bam under BB Ki Vines Productions, the show continues to be penned by the talented writer duo Hussain Dalal & Abbas Dalal. Bhuvan Bam reprises his role as Vasant Gawde, joined by Shriya Pilgaonkar, Mahesh Manjrekar, Jaaved Jaaferi, Deven Bhojani, Shilpa Shukla, Prathmesh Parab, and Nitya Mathur in pivotal roles.

This season explores the thin line between blessing and curse as Vasya navigates a world where his actions have far-reaching consequences. With higher stakes and deeper emotional complexity, Taaza Khabar Season 2 promises to deliver a gripping tale of redemption, morality, and the human spirit's resilience in the face of adversity.

#TaazaKhabarSeason2 #BBKiVinesProductions #BhuvanBam

ABOUT:
Bhuvan Bam, a multi-talented artist, returns as Vasya in this thrilling new season. To stay updated with Bhuvan's journey and behind-the-scenes content, follow him on:

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Teaser
snippet.description:
Be There and Be Square. #MinecraftMovie - only in theaters 2025

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, ‚ÄúA Minecraft Movie,‚Äù directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time.

The film also stars Emma Myers (‚ÄúWednesday‚Äù), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (‚ÄúThe Color Purple‚Äù), Sebastian Eugene Hansen (‚ÄúJust Mercy, ‚ÄúLisey‚Äôs Story‚Äù), with Jennifer Coolidge.

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesn‚Äôt just help you craft, it‚Äôs essential to one‚Äôs survival!  Four misfits‚ÄîGarrett ‚ÄúThe Garbage Man‚Äù Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)‚Äîfind themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination.  To get back home, they‚Äôll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black).  Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative‚Ä¶the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (‚ÄúNinety-Five Senses,‚Äù ‚ÄúNacho Libre‚Äù) directed, with Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Olafsson and Vu Bui producing, and Todd Hallowell, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza, Jonathan Spaihts, Pete Chiappetta, Andrew Lary and Anthony Tittanegro executive producing.

The director‚Äôs creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (‚Äú127 Hours,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransformers: Rise of the Beasts‚Äù), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (‚ÄúThe Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Meg‚Äù), editor James Thomas (‚ÄúPok√©mon: Detective Pikachu‚Äù, the ‚ÄúBorat‚Äù films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (‚ÄúThe Jungle Book,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), and costume designer Amanda Neale (‚ÄúThe Meg,‚Äù ‚ÄúWhat We Do in the Shadows‚Äù).  Casting is by Rachel Tenner.  The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (‚ÄúThor: Ragnarok,‚Äù the ‚ÄúLEGO¬Æ‚Äù movies).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/Moj√§ng Aktiebolag Production, A Jared Hess Film, ‚ÄúA Minecraft Movie.‚Äù  The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Chaduvu Biddalu || Episode 02 || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Chaduvu Biddalu Episode 02 MCM
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu releases its new episode Chaduvu Biddalu. In this engaging filmymoji video, the middle-class character Madhu and the Naatu Guntala gang navigate their first day in a classroom setting. As the professors commence their lessons, the gang's apprehension about academic pressures mounts, leading them to contemplate abandoning their studies altogether. This relatable narrative captures the challenges faced by students in balancing education and personal concerns, making it a compelling watch for audiences.

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.

snippet.title: Visfot | Official Trailer | Streaming 6 September | JioCinema Premium
snippet.description:
Visfot is a gripping crime thriller that explores the dangerous consequences of deceit and poor choices. The film follows the lives of two families, one living in a Mumbai slum and the other in a luxurious high-rise, whoseSS paths intertwine unexpectedly. A series of events leads to a tragic explosion, leaving one man wrongly accused of a crime he didn't commit. As he fights to clear his name, he uncovers a web of corruption and deceit that threatens to destroy everything he holds dear.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 38 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 3rd September - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.title: What is NASA Searching for in DEEP SEA
snippet.description:
Teeth aligners by toothsi close teeth gaps and straighten crooked teeth. Book your FREE teeth scan now - https://toothsi.makeo.app/3MpQeoF
Discount Code: GET24TS

What is NASA searching for in the deep ocean? Yes, what secrets lie 10 km beneath the ocean's surface that NASA is desperately trying to uncover?

Few people know that just off the coast of Florida, at a depth of 20 meters in the ocean, lies the world's only underwater lab called Aquarius Reef Base. Every year, NASA sends 5-6 researchers and astronauts‚Äîyes, astronauts‚Äîto this lab for several weeks as part of a special project called Project NEEMO (NASA‚Äôs Extreme Environment Mission Operations). These NASA scientists are referred to as "Aquanauts." But that's not all. NASA also has an autonomous underwater vehicle named ORPHEUS, which is diving 10 km deep into the ocean to conduct research. But why is a space agency like NASA working in the depths of the ocean? After all, the U.S. has a separate organization, NOAA (National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration), specifically for ocean research.
What is so urgent that a 2-month deadline has been set? Let's try to understand what's going on in the minds of NASA scientists and whether we should be concerned about it.

snippet.description:

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.title: Epic Tabletop RPG Adventure Awaits! Clash of Clans New Season
snippet.description:
Step into a world of magic, mystery, and epic quests! Our latest season brings the thrill of tabletop RPGs to life. Whether you're a seasoned adventurer or a new hero, this is your chance to prove your mettle. With new challenges, exclusive rewards, and endless adventure, the path to glory starts here!

Learn more about what is to come: https://supercell.com/en/games/clashofclans/blog/news/tabletop-rpg-adventure-awaits/


Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ‚ñ∫ https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ‚ñ∫ https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ‚ñ∫ https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ‚ñ∫ https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-¬≠filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

In this powerful talk, #Salhabeegum , a #contentcreator  and #sociaworker , shares her courageous story of overcoming life's toughest challenges. Having faced #depression  and loss in her personal life, including the struggles of #motherhood  , #business  setbacks, and the loss of her father, Salha opens up about her darkest moments. But what makes her story truly remarkable is her unwavering determination and resilience. She reveals how she turned her struggles into strengths and found a way to rise above adversity, ultimately achieving success in her career as a student with an #llb  degree. Join us as Salha shares her inspiring journey of transformation, offering valuable lessons on how to overcome obstacles, build resilience, and find purpose in the face of adversity.

Subscribe to Josh Talks Malayalam for more inspiring stories of individuals who have broken free from societal expectations and achieved success in their way.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalis by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags-to-riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women‚Äôs rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

In this powerful talk, #Salhabeegum , a #contentcreator  and #sociaworker , shares her courageous story of overcoming life's toughest challenges. Having faced #depression  and loss in her personal life, including the struggles of #motherhood  , #business  setbacks, and the loss of her father, Salha opens up about her darkest moments. But what makes her story truly remarkable is her unwavering determination and resilience. She reveals how she turned her struggles into strengths and found a way to rise above adversity, ultimately achieving success in her career as a student with an #llb  degree. Join us as Salha shares her inspiring journey of transformation, offering valuable lessons on how to overcome obstacles, build resilience, and find purpose in the face of adversity.

Subscribe to Josh Talks Malayalam for more inspiring stories of individuals who have broken free from societal expectations and achieved success in their way.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalis by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags-to-riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women‚Äôs rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

snippet.title: Vinayagar Chathurthi Pillayarpatti Modagam Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make modagam recipe in tamil. This modagam recipe is a large kozhukattai which is made from pacharisi, moong dal, coconut and jaggery. This sweet recipe is popular during the vinayagar chathurthi festival. This sweet recipe is very quick and easy to make and these kolukattai are very tasty.
#modagamrecipe #kozhukkattai #kollukattai 

Friends please do try this modagam kozhukattai recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
Makes 12 large Kozhukattai:
I have used 125 ml cup to measure all the ingredients
1 cup Raw Rice (100g)ingredients)
1/2 cup Moong dal (50g)
3/4 cup grated coconut
2 cup Jaggery (200g)
1/5 tbsp Ghee
3 cup Water

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Homemade Maharashtrian Sunday Brunch at Sharvari Wagh‚Äôs Dadar Home | Ep 140 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
Be The First To Watch All Videos. Download the CurlyTales App:
https://curlytale.page.link/DwNd

In this episode of Sunday Brunch Presented By @Samsung Galaxy Book4 Series, we‚Äôre joined by the fabulous Sharvari Wagh! 

From winning Fresh Face to becoming India's National Crush, Sharvari has taken Bollywood by storm with her roles & her dazzling smile!
We visited her beautiful Dadar home overlooking the sea link and had a heartfelt chat about her memories of Dadar, her love for food, and her journey to Bollywood, including winning the Best Debut Award and her upcoming projects. 

But that‚Äôs not all! We also indulged in a delicious homemade Maharashtrian feast featuring 7-step Misal, Kothimbir Vadi, Piyush, Shakarpare, Besan Ladoo, and more‚Äîbringing the true essence of a Marathi Mulgi to life.

The fun continued with a quirky game where I used the Samsung Galaxy Book4 Pro 360's Multi Control Feature to drag emojis onto the screen. The twist? Sharvari had to deliver famous Bollywood dialogues based on the emojis‚Äîin Marathi! And we topped it off with a thrilling fan interaction call.

Sharvari‚Äôs love for Maharashtrian food proves she‚Äôs a typical Marathi Mulgi through and through. We had a blast at brunch, and we hope you enjoy watching it as much as we did filming it!

snippet.description:
